---
title: Old Bay-Spiced Salmon & Sweet Potato Cakes with Tomato-Arugula Salad
description: Inspired by Maryland crab cakes, this recipe calls on everyone's favorite Old Bay seasoning for serious flavor. Creamy sweet potato binds together flaky salmon, sautéed aromatics, and light panko breadcrumbs for tender pan-seared salmon cakes.
